<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id56d5ff9c-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02" identifier="/us/usc/t14/s3732"><num value="3732">§ 3732.</num><heading> Applicability of this subchapter</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter applies only to the Reserve; except that it does not apply to a temporary member of the Reserve.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id56d5ff9d-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/96/322/s1">Pub. L. 96–322, § 1</ref>, <date date="1980-08-04">Aug. 4, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/1007">94 Stat. 1007</ref>, § 721; renumbered § 3732, <ref href="/us/pl/115/282/tI/s118/b">Pub. L. 115–282, title I, § 118(b)</ref>, <date date="2018-12-04">Dec. 4, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/4233">132 Stat. 4233</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id56d5ff9e-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id56d5ff9f-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id56d5ffa0-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Provisions similar to those in this section were contained in <ref href="/us/usc/t14/s771">section 771 of this title</ref> prior to the complete revision of former chapter 21 of this title by <ref href="/us/pl/96/322">Pub. L. 96–322</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id56d5ffa1-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—<ref href="/us/pl/115/282">Pub. L. 115–282</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t14/s721">section 721 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
